OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning with some
OL,6,Foccasional rain or drizzle, perhaps
OL,7,Fturning more persistent for a time
OL,8,Fearlier in the morning. Becoming
OL,9,Fgenerally drier and brighter through
OL,10,Fthe afternoon with a few showers,
OL,11,Fheavy at times.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FQuite cloudy with scattered
OL,14,Fshowers in the evening. Generally
OL,15,Fbecoming drier through the night but
OL,16,Fstill a few showers around. Windy
OL,17,Faround the coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
