OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloudy and windy with rain
OL,6,Fthrough the morning, heavy at times.
OL,7,FBecoming dry but still cloudy in the
OL,8,Fearly afternoon, before bright spells
OL,9,Fdevelop later with the odd shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fwith some rain Friday morning,
OL,13,Fbrighter with the odd shower later.
OL,14,FDry start Saturday before further rain
OL,15,Fspreading later. Cloudy and breezy
OL,16,Fwith outbreaks of rain on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
